title: WSHQ barometer removed
description: Reinstalled barometer while getting station back online.  Worked for 6 days, but with sudden drops to 500mb on the following timestamps:  1/16/2014 8:55 1/19/2014 13:45 to 1/19/2014 14:20 1/20/2014 11:50 1/21/2014 11:55 to 1/21/2014 12:00 Then it cut-out, flatlining at 500mb again.  Update 2/25/2014 by Chris Wong: After installing the new CR1000 the barometer was not giving good values. After running for a day it was still not giving good values. It was removed from the HQ weather station at 3:12 on 2/25/2014. (SN H4460016) incident report migrated from SensorDB.

external_refs.identifier: WSHQ barometer failed again; see incident report IR_109
